38
00:02:01.100 --> 00:02:04.620
often ending up on the beach in the evening beside a

39
00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.539
beachside fire.

40
00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:10.320
But that was 35 years ago, and it wasn't in New Zealand.

41
00:02:10.741 --> 00:02:14.400
We grew up in Guernsey. Guernsey's a small island in the

42
00:02:14.420 --> 00:02:15.140
English Channel.

43
00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:20.200
